(4, 1, 'О компании', '<div class=\"about-promo promo\" data-anim=\"group\"><div class=\"promo__in inner inner_mob\"><div class=\"promo__left\"><h1 class=\"title-h1 about-promo__title\" data-anim=\"stagger-items\">ESL Global (English second language)</h1><div class=\"about-promo__info-block info-block js-info-block\"><div class=\"info-block__line js-info-block-line\"></div><div class=\"info-block__text\" data-anim=\"stagger-items\">Помогаем всем желающим устроиться на работу в Китай учителем английского</div></div></div></div><div class=\"buble-img\" data-anim=\"stagger-element\" data-anim-element-delay=\"0.4\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/static/img/about-bubles/1.png\" /></div></div><div class=\"about-text\" data-section=\"about-text\"><div class=\"buble-img buble-img_tleft\" data-anim=\"group\"><img alt=\"\" data-anim=\"stagger-element\" src=\"/static/img/about-bubles/2.png\" /></div><div class=\"buble-img buble-img_tright\" data-anim=\"group\"><img alt=\"alt\" data-anim=\"stagger-element\" src=\"/static/img/about-bubles/3.png\" /></div><div class=\"about-text__in inner inner_mob\"><div class=\"pull-right\" data-anim=\"group\"><h2 class=\"title-h2 about-text__title\" data-anim=\"stagger-items\">Почему мы хороши в своём деле</h2></div><div class=\"article about-text__article\" data-anim=\"group\"><div data-anim=\"stagger-items\"><p>Компания ESL Global была создана в 2013 году, как оператор трудоустройства в Китае в сфере преподавания. Организованная нами программа является результатом тщательного изучения и понимания данной индустрии во всех ее аспектах. С момента основания и по сей день мы продолжаем учиться и совершенствовать свой продукт, добиваясь еще большего комфорта и выгоды для наших клиентов.</p></div><div class=\"article__last\"><div data-anim=\"stagger-items\"><p>Мы предусмотрели всё:</p></div></div><ol class=\"advantages about__advantages \" type=\"1\">	<li class=\"advantages__item\">	<div class=\"advantages__icon\"><svg class=\"icon icon-support_1\"> <use xlink:href=\"/img/sprite.svg#icon-support_1\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\"></use> </svg></div>	<div class=\"advantages__text\"><strong>Экономия денег, размерянная жизнь в Китае без надобности выезжать каждый месяц:</strong><br />	Открываем долгосрочные визы в Китай для всех желающих поехать по программе и в качестве сопровождения.</div>	</li>	<li class=\"advantages__item\">	<div class=\"advantages__icon\"><svg class=\"icon icon-support_1\"> <use xlink:href=\"/img/sprite.svg#icon-support_1\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\"></use> </svg></div>	<div class=\"advantages__text\"><strong>Гарантированный комфорт проживания:</strong><br />	Мы лично контролируем стандарты качества жилья для наших клиентов.</div>	</li>	<li class=\"advantages__item\">	<div class=\"advantages__icon\"><svg class=\"icon icon-support_1\"> <use xlink:href=\"/img/sprite.svg#icon-support_1\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\"></use> </svg></div>	<div class=\"advantages__text\"><strong>Вы не останетесь один:</strong><br />	По прилету в Китай, каждого клиента опекает и поддерживает целая команда<br />	менеджеров и ассистентов для решения<br />	и помощи в рабочих и бытовых<br />	вопросах.</div>	</li>	<li class=\"advantages__item\">	<div class=\"advantages__icon\"><svg class=\"icon icon-support_1\"> <use xlink:href=\"/img/sprite.svg#icon-support_1\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\"></use> </svg></div>	<div class=\"advantages__text\"><strong>Будете в курсе всех новостей и событий:</strong><br />	Уникальное приложение, разработанное специально для<br />	наших клиентов. Следите за всем актуальным, что касается: Китая, сферы преподавания и лично Вас.</div>	</li></ol></div></div><div class=\"buble-img buble-img_bleft\" data-anim=\"group\"><img alt=\"alt\" data-anim=\"stagger-element\" src=\"/static/img/about-bubles/4.png\" /></div><div class=\"buble-img buble-img_bright\" data-anim=\"group\"><img alt=\"alt\" data-anim=\"stagger-element\" src=\"/static/img/about-bubles/5.png\" /></div></div>', 'Помогаем всем желающим устроиться на работу в Китай учителем английского', 'Мы были первыми в Украине, у кого получилось подойти к работе в Китае системно: отвечать за жилье и трудоустройство, брать на себя рутину с документами и поддерживать связь с клиентами 24/7.', ''),
(4, 2, 'About us', '<div class=\"about-promo promo\" data-anim=\"group\"><div class=\"promo__in inner inner_mob\"><div class=\"promo__left\"><h1 class=\"title-h1 about-promo__title\" data-anim=\"stagger-items\">ESL Global (English Second Language)</h1><div class=\"about-promo__info-block info-block js-info-block\"><div class=\"info-block__line js-info-block-line\"></div><div class=\"info-block__text\" data-anim=\"stagger-items\">Your trustworthy partner</div></div></div></div><div class=\"buble-img\" data-anim=\"stagger-element\" data-anim-element-delay=\"0.4\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/static/img/about-bubles/1.png\" /></div></div><div class=\"about-text\" data-section=\"about-text\"><div class=\"buble-img buble-img_tleft\" data-anim=\"group\"><img alt=\"\" data-anim=\"stagger-element\" src=\"/static/img/about-bubles/2.png\" /></div><div class=\"buble-img buble-img_tright\" data-anim=\"group\"><img alt=\"alt\" data-anim=\"stagger-element\" src=\"/static/img/about-bubles/3.png\" /></div><div class=\"about-text__in inner inner_mob\"><div class=\"pull-right\" data-anim=\"group\"><h2 class=\"title-h2 about-text__title\" data-anim=\"stagger-items\">What makes us good?</h2></div><div class=\"article about-text__article\" data-anim=\"group\"><div data-anim=\"stagger-items\"><p>ESL Global has been established in 2013 as a third party employment provider in China. Our company is a result of clear understanding and a great passion for ESL teaching industry in China. We have put all the knowledge and experience, gained by dealing with various issues that had come up during our work. We constantly learn, improve and develop our skills for even better service.</p></div><div class=\"article__last\"><div data-anim=\"stagger-items\"></div></div><ol class=\"advantages about__advantages \" type=\"1\">	<li class=\"advantages__item\">	<div class=\"advantages__icon\"><svg class=\"icon icon-support_1\"> <use xlink:href=\"/img/sprite.svg#icon-support_1\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\"></use> </svg></div>	<div class=\"advantages__text\"><strong>Have a peaceful and smooth stay in China:</strong><br />	Long term visas for all the participants and their friends/relatives to go with.</div>	</li>	<li class=\"advantages__item\">	<div class=\"advantages__icon\"><svg class=\"icon icon-support_1\"> <use xlink:href=\"/img/sprite.svg#icon-support_1\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\"></use> </svg></div>	<div class=\"advantages__text\"><strong>Comfort living - guaranteed:</strong><br />	We personally choose and evaluate the quality level of provided housing to our teachers.</div>	</li>	<li class=\"advantages__item\">	<div class=\"advantages__icon\"><svg class=\"icon icon-support_1\"> <use xlink:href=\"/img/sprite.svg#icon-support_1\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\"></use> </svg></div>	<div class=\"advantages__text\"><strong>You won&rsquo;t be lonely:</strong><br />	Since the first day of arrival you&rsquo;ll be surrounded by our numerous managers and assistants to help you with any working or leisure stuff.</div>	</li>	<li class=\"advantages__item\">	<div class=\"advantages__icon\"><svg class=\"icon icon-support_1\"> <use xlink:href=\"/img/sprite.svg#icon-support_1\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\"></use> </svg></div>	<div class=\"advantages__text\"><strong>Stay up to date:</strong><br />	Our unique private App will keep you updated with everything you need to know while in China.</div>	</li></ol></div></div><div class=\"buble-img buble-img_bleft\" data-anim=\"group\"><img alt=\"alt\" data-anim=\"stagger-element\" src=\"/static/img/about-bubles/4.png\" /></div><div class=\"buble-img buble-img_bright\" data-anim=\"group\"><img alt=\"alt\" data-anim=\"stagger-element\" src=\"/static/img/about-bubles/5.png\" /></div></div>', 'ESL About company', 'ESL About company', 'ESL About company'),
(5, 1, 'Приложения для преподавателей', '<div class=\"app-promo\" data-anim=\"group\" data-section=\"\">    <div class=\"app-promo__in inner\">      <div class=\"app-promo__container\"><h1 class=\"title-h1 app-promo__title\" data-anim=\"stagger-items\"> Скоро будет доступно приложение ESL Global </h1>        <div class=\"info-block info-block_long app-promo__info-block js-info-block\">          <div class=\"info-block__line js-info-block-line\"></div>          <div class=\"info-block__text\" data-anim=\"stagger-items\"> Социальная сеть для наших учителей английского в Китае</div>        </div>      </div>      <div class=\"app-promo__btns store\"></div>    </div>    <div class=\"buble-img\" data-anim=\"stagger-element\" data-anim-element-duration=\"0.4\" data-anim-element-delay=\"0.4\"><img src=\"/static/img/app-bubles/1.png\" alt=\"alt\">      <div class=\"buble-img__phone\" data-anim=\"stagger-element\" data-anim-element-delay=\"0.4\"><img src=\"/uploads/thumb/0/application_phone/9-phone.png\" alt=\"image\"></div>    </div>  </div>  <div class=\"capabilities\">    <div class=\"capabilities__main\" data-anim=\"group\"><h2 class=\"capabilities__title title-h1\" data-anim=\"stagger-items\"> Возможности приложения </h2>      <div class=\"buble-img\"><img src=\"/static/img/app-bubles/2.png\" alt=\"\"></div>    </div>    <div class=\"capability right capability_a\" data-section=\"\" data-anim=\"group\">      <div class=\"buble-img\" data-anim=\"stagger-element\"><img src=\"/static/img/app-bubles/3.png\" alt=\"alt\">        <div class=\"buble-img__phone\"><img src=\"/uploads/thumb/0/application_phone/10-phone.png\" alt=\"alt 1\"></div>      </div>      <div class=\"inner inner_mob\">        <div class=\"capability__item\"><h3 class=\"capability__title title-h2\" data-anim=\"stagger-items\"> События в Китае </h3>          <div class=\"capability__text\" data-anim=\"stagger-items\"> Вы сможете отслеживать новости и происшествия, подсказывает даты праздников и других событий.</div>        </div>      </div>    </div>    <div class=\"capability left capability_b\" data-section=\"\" data-anim=\"group\">      <div class=\"buble-img\" data-anim=\"stagger-element\"><img src=\"/static/img/app-bubles/4.png\" alt=\"alt\">        <div class=\"buble-img__phone\"><img src=\"/uploads/thumb/0/application_phone/11-phone.png\" alt=\"alt 2\"></div>      </div>      <div class=\"inner inner_mob\">        <div class=\"capability__item\"><h3 class=\"capability__title title-h2\" data-anim=\"stagger-items\"> Кафе, кинотеатры, рестораны </h3>          <div class=\"capability__text\" data-anim=\"stagger-items\"> Рекомендует проверенные рестораны и кафе, фитнес-клубы, ресурсы по заказу билетов.</div>        </div>      </div>    </div>    <div class=\"capability right capability_c\" data-section=\"\" data-anim=\"group\">      <div class=\"buble-img\" data-anim=\"stagger-element\"><img src=\"/static/img/app-bubles/5.png\" alt=\"alt\">        <div class=\"buble-img__phone\"><img src=\"/uploads/thumb/0/application_phone/12-phone.png\" alt=\"image\"></div>      </div>      <div class=\"inner inner_mob\">        <div class=\"capability__item\"><h3 class=\"capability__title title-h2\" data-anim=\"stagger-items\"> Деловые знакомства </h3>          <div class=\"capability__text\" data-anim=\"stagger-items\"><p>Объединяет в чат людей из разных городов для обмена опытом, фото и личных встреч.</p></div>        </div>      </div>    </div>    <div class=\"capability left capability_d\" data-section=\"\" data-anim=\"group\">      <div class=\"buble-img\" data-anim=\"stagger-element\"><img src=\"/static/img/app-bubles/6.png\" alt=\"alt\">        <div class=\"buble-img__phone\"><img src=\"/uploads/thumb/0/application_phone/13-phone.png\" alt=\"image\"></div>      </div>      <div class=\"inner inner_mob\">        <div class=\"capability__item\"><h3 class=\"capability__title title-h2\" data-anim=\"stagger-items\"> Уведомления от кураторов </h3>          <div class=\"capability__text\" data-anim=\"stagger-items\"><p>Позволяет куратору общаться со своей группой: о визах, работе или вариантах отдыха.</p></div>        </div>      </div>    </div>    <div class=\"capability right capability_e\" data-section=\"\" data-anim=\"group\">      <div class=\"inner-capability inner-capability_mob\">        <div class=\"capability__item\"><h3 class=\"capability__title title-h2\" data-anim=\"stagger-items\"> С приложением ESL Global жизнь в Китае станет еще удобнее </h3>          <div class=\"buble-img\" data-anim=\"stagger-element\"><img src=\"/static/img/app-bubles/7.png\" alt=\"alt\">            <div class=\"buble-img__phone\"><img src=\"/uploads/thumb/0/application_phone/14-phone.png\" alt=\"image\"></div>          </div>          <div class=\"capability__text\" data-anim=\"stagger-items\"><p>Приложение в разработке</p></div>        </div>      </div>    </div>    <div class=\"inner \" data-anim=\"group\">      <div class=\"capabilities__btns\">        <div class=\"store store_right\"></div>      </div>    </div>  </div>', 'Приложение для преподавателей ESL Global', 'Социальная сеть для наших учителей английского в Китае', 'Приложение для преподавателей ESL Global'),
(5, 2, 'Our app', '<div class=\"app-promo\" data-anim=\"group\" data-section=\"\"><div class=\"app-promo__in inner\"><div class=\"app-promo__container\"><h1 class=\"title-h1 app-promo__title\" data-anim=\"stagger-items\">Application for teachers</h1><div class=\"info-block info-block_long app-promo__info-block js-info-block\"><div class=\"info-block__line js-info-block-line\"></div><div class=\"info-block__text\" data-anim=\"stagger-items\">Meet our new private social network for ESL Global participants in China. Coming soon</div></div></div><div class=\"app-promo__btns store\"></div></div><div class=\"buble-img\" data-anim=\"stagger-element\" data-anim-element-delay=\"0.4\" data-anim-element-duration=\"0.4\"><img alt=\"alt\" src=\"/static/img/app-bubles/1.png\" /><div class=\"buble-img__phone\" data-anim=\"stagger-element\" data-anim-element-delay=\"0.4\"><img alt=\"image\" src=\"/uploads/thumb/0/application_phone/9-phone.png\" /></div></div></div><div class=\"capabilities\"><div class=\"capabilities__main\" data-anim=\"group\"><h2 class=\"capabilities__title title-h1\" data-anim=\"stagger-items\">Explore more</h2><div class=\"buble-img\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/static/img/app-bubles/2.png\" /></div></div><div class=\"capability right capability_a\" data-anim=\"group\" data-section=\"\"><div class=\"buble-img\" data-anim=\"stagger-element\"><img alt=\"alt\" src=\"/static/img/app-bubles/3.png\" /><div class=\"buble-img__phone\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/thumb/0/application_phone/10-phone.png\" /></div></div><div class=\"inner inner_mob\"><div class=\"capability__item\"><h3 class=\"capability__title title-h2\" data-anim=\"stagger-items\">China express:</h3><div class=\"capability__text\" data-anim=\"stagger-items\">Stay tuned in: See what happens around you, track the news feed, be aware of the biggest deals in town.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"capability left capability_b\" data-anim=\"group\" data-section=\"\"><div class=\"buble-img\" data-anim=\"stagger-element\"><img alt=\"alt\" src=\"/static/img/app-bubles/4.png\" /><div class=\"buble-img__phone\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/thumb/0/application_phone/11-phone.png\" /></div></div><div class=\"inner inner_mob\"><div class=\"capability__item\"><h3 class=\"capability__title title-h2\" data-anim=\"stagger-items\">Leisure department:</h3><div class=\"capability__text\" data-anim=\"stagger-items\">Check our recommended restaurants, bars, cinemas, gyms and various spectacular spots.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"capability right capability_c\" data-anim=\"group\" data-section=\"\"><div class=\"buble-img\" data-anim=\"stagger-element\"><img alt=\"alt\" src=\"/static/img/app-bubles/5.png\" /><div class=\"buble-img__phone\"><img alt=\"image\" src=\"/uploads/thumb/0/application_phone/12-phone.png\" /></div></div><div class=\"inner inner_mob\"><div class=\"capability__item\"><h3 class=\"capability__title title-h2\" data-anim=\"stagger-items\">Global connection:</h3><div class=\"capability__text\" data-anim=\"stagger-items\">Make new international friends from different cities all over China, exchange your photos and moments, share the experiences.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"capability left capability_d\" data-anim=\"group\" data-section=\"\"><div class=\"buble-img\" data-anim=\"stagger-element\"><img alt=\"alt\" src=\"/static/img/app-bubles/6.png\" /><div class=\"buble-img__phone\"><img alt=\"image\" src=\"/uploads/thumb/0/application_phone/13-phone.png\" /></div></div><div class=\"inner inner_mob\"><div class=\"capability__item\"><h3 class=\"capability__title title-h2\" data-anim=\"stagger-items\">Notification center:</h3><div class=\"capability__text\" data-anim=\"stagger-items\">Stay notified about all the work-related news/events, consult with our managers for private issues.</div></div></div></div><div class=\"capability right capability_e\" data-anim=\"group\" data-section=\"\"><div class=\"inner-capability inner-capability_mob\"><div class=\"capability__i